User Stories

User

As a user, I want to register using my mobile number so that I can quickly start using the app.

As a user, I want to view nearby available bikes so that I can book instantly.

As a user, I want real-time fare estimation so that I know the cost before booking.

As a user, I want to pay digitally so that the process is seamless.

As a user, I want to track my ride so that I feel secure.

Vendor

As a vendor, I want to get booking alerts so that I can accept rides quickly.

As a vendor, I want to track ongoing rides so that I can monitor my fleet.

As a vendor, I want to view earning history so that I can manage finances.

Admin

As an admin, I want to manage vendors so that only verified providers operate.

As an admin, I want to view reports so that I can track business performance.

As an admin, I want to handle disputes so that user satisfaction is maintained.

4️⃣ Acceptance Criteria (GIVEN – WHEN – THEN)

User Booking

Given user is logged in
When they request a bike
Then the system shall show available bikes within 3 km radius.

Vendor Accept Ride

Given vendor is online
When a booking request arrives
Then the vendor shall be able to accept within 30 seconds.

Payment

Given ride is completed
When the user chooses a payment method
Then the payment should process successfully and generate a receipt.
